{marker remarks}{...}
{title:备注}

{pstd}
备注呈现于以下标题之下：

            {help graph editor##quickstart:快速启动}
            {help graph editor##introduction:介绍}
            {help graph editor##start_stop:启动和停止图形编辑器}
            {help graph editor##tools:工具}
    	        {help graph editor##pointer:指针工具}
	        {help graph editor##text_tool:添加文本工具}
	        {help graph editor##line_tool:添加线条工具}
	        {help graph editor##marker_tool:添加标记工具}
	        {help graph editor##grid_edit_tool:网格编辑工具}
            {help graph editor##object_browser:对象浏览器}
            {help graph editor##contextual_menus:右键菜单或上下文菜单}
            {help graph editor##standard_toolbar:标准工具栏}
            {help graph editor##main_menu:主要图形编辑器菜单}
            {help graph editor##grid_editing:网格编辑}
